" LESS {{{
hi lessVariable             ctermfg=11
hi! link lessVariableValue  Normal

"}}}
" NERDTree {{{
hi! link NERDTreeHelp      Comment
hi! link NERDTreeExecFile  String

"}}}
" Vimwiki {{{
